title: Kelenate® (Baked with Love) Kraft, 80 Pieces, 2inches, Round, Unique Designs, Self-Adhesive Stickers Labels Roll Decor Tags for Baking Packages, Homemade Gifts, Small Business Supplies
bullets: ["[Handmade with Love Stickers] - Made of thicker premium kraft paper, thick and durable, not easy to break. title: Kelenate® 2000 Piece Color 12mm (0.5 Inch) Round Dot Sticker Self Adhesive Labels Writable Surface for Kids Activity, File Classification, Calendar Planner (Orange)
bullets: ["✅ Package Contents: This package includes 2000 colored dot stickers, ensuring you have more than enough for extensive usage across various applications.","✅ Broad Utility: Suitable for numerous environments including offices, homes, and meetings. title: Buylogy® (12) Warning Reflective Stickers Safety Reflective Stickers Night Visibility Adhesive Stickers Waterproof Reflective Tape Stickers for Vehicle Motorcycle Bicycle, 1.18 x 3.25 Inch
bullets: ["Brightness Upgrade: with the full prism reflection technology, the car warning reflective stickers have a good transmittance advantage, clear and reflective in the night, which can improve vehicle and reduce the occurrence of accidents, effectively protecting people's safety when driving at intersections, turning at corners and more","Sturdy Material: the night warning stickers adopt a quality DG3 film and self-adhesive construction, weather resistant and waterproof, lightweight but strong, wear and tear resistant, and their good viscosity can provide you with a long time service","Simple Operation: the installation of the night visibility adhesive sticker is quite convenient, first you need to clean and dry the surface which needs to be pasted, then peel off the protective film of the safety sticker and paste the sticker according to the surface you are using","Adequate Amount: there are many pieces visibility reflective stickers in 3 colors in the package, red, yellow, silver, each of which measures approx. 1.18 x 3.25 Inch, which can meet your different using needs, you can also share some of them with your family members, classmates, neighbors and so on","Multiple Purposes: the waterproof reflective tape stickers have various usages, which are not only suitable for many vehicles, like cars, trucks, scooters, motorcycles, bicycle, trailer and yacht, but also for helmets, mailbox, fence, backpacks, jacket, running vest when you are hiking, cycling, traveling, etc"]

bullets: ["✔ Reflective Material - The vinyl reflective material will have a reflective effect when illuminated with light. This high-quality vinyl sticker will not crack, fade and peel.
